{"tid":2193252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"你班崇日撚收皮! 港式餐蛋麵屌打日本拉麵 !!!!","createTime":"2020-09-07T16:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T11:26:18.000Z","uid":353419,"like":10,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d44394d46bc0f4cb236c0d5f482a1476edb123","tid":2193252,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:21:09.000Z","msg":"自從去日本拉麵競技場, 試完各地拉麵,<br />\n我發覺好好食, 但食得多會厭, <br />\n<br />\n返香港食茶記, 驚覺餐蛋麵先係最好食, 中學日日食都唔厭<br />\n你可能覺得我假膠, 但我好認真同你講,<br />\n<br />\n你覺得餐蛋麵劣食,係因為你懶係受過高等教育,懶係有學識認為日本拉麵好精深, <br />\n就等於長輩由細到大同你講日本人好細心好認真, 所以香港人自細崇日.<br />\n<br />\n兩塊午餐肉,一塊蛋, 一舊平價公仔麵, 製作粗劣但出奇好食,<br />\n加兩滴辣淑油, 味道即刻升華,<br />\n呢啲咪叫化腐朽為神奇 , 香港茶餐廳世界第一."},{"pid":"e86230a5019d8d5c7f97340cfc45791bd22adfc9","tid":2193252,"uid":364916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8671562775ae08ca091dc814345c15d7972e51bb","tid":2193252,"uid":202121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"Conform food 咋"},{"pid":"d97997f7b6262657943cdc7955c80cd9bd3aa8c2","tid":2193252,"uid":18948,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"公仔麵都係日本嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d830678c69a1751d141acbe697ba344d3e55fe","tid":2193252,"uid":229127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:05:00.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"f34de2efe152f815181dfba6beff593012a4ad3b","tid":2193252,"uid":78429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"係都拎叉鵝瀨雲吞麵呢啲嚟比"},{"pid":"3fb113256b3135e1726397eb8f172b11ecb043c4","tid":2193252,"uid":50216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"係都牛腩河"},{"pid":"563f305d75af415dc244dc459ca2142b2f66b0e2","tid":2193252,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r